utest samePaths eqedge (eqPaths g 7 2) [[l7, l8], [l2, l8], [l1, l8]] with true in
utest samePaths eqedge (eqPaths g 7 10) [[l5, l6, l7, l8], [l2, l8], [l1, l8]] with true in

